OL,3,CUnearthing the past: How a daughter's
OL,4,Cdevotion exposed her mother's murder
OL,6,FMeeting at a hotel in the town centre,
OL,7,FI am instantly impressed by her quiet
OL,8,Fconfidence and assured manner in front
OL,9,Fof the camera. Speaking through an
OL,10,Finterpreter, she quietly and
OL,11,Fthoughtfully answers my questions.
OL,13,FI had got in touch with Katarzyna
OL,14,Fthrough a Polish missing persons
OL,15,Fcharity she had been working with in
OL,16,Fthe search for her mother Izabela.
OL,18,FFrom the outset, she was keen to talk,
OL,19,Feven though Derbyshire Police had told
OL,20,FITV News Central that she had no wish
OL,21,Fto do any media interviews.
