OL,3,CUnearthing the past: How a daughter's
OL,4,Cdevotion exposed her mother's murder
OL,6,FIn particular, she wanted to tell the
OL,7,Fworld what her mother was really like,
OL,8,Fafter hearing so many "lies" told
OL,9,Fabout her by Anna Podedworna in court.
OL,10,FShe recalls fondly the special loving
OL,11,Frelationship she had with her mother
OL,12,Fand their many trips to the seaside.
OL,14,FDuring those fifteen long years when
OL,15,Fher mother was missing, Katarzyna
OL,16,Fsuspected that Podedworna might have
OL,17,Fhad something to do with her
OL,18,Fdisappearance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
