OL,3,CUnearthing the past: How a daughter's
OL,4,Cdevotion exposed her mother's murder
OL,6,FAnd it's no exaggeration to say that,
OL,7,Fwithout her tireless efforts to find
OL,8,Fout the truth, Podedworna could still
OL,9,Fbe free and Izabela's body could still
OL,10,Fbe buried in a back garden in Derby.
OL,12,FKatarzyna is keen to acknowledge the
OL,13,Fimportant role of the Polish media and
OL,14,Fin particular TV journalist Rafal
OL,15,FZalewski, but it was her tenacity and
OL,16,Fpersistence which finally led to
OL,17,FPodedworna's downfall.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
