OL,3,CUnearthing the past: How a daughter's
OL,4,Cdevotion exposed her mother's murder
OL,6,FShe's less complimentary about the
OL,7,Fefforts of Derbyshire Police when the
OL,8,Ffamily first reported Izabela missing
OL,9,Fin 2010. They made some enquiries, she
OL,10,Fsays, but could have done more.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the end of the trial, the
OL,12,Fofficer in charge of the case says
OL,13,Fhe's confident the force did as much
OL,14,Fas it could in the face of
OL,15,FPodedworna's lies, but says it will
OL,16,Freview its actions back then.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
