OL,3,CUnearthing the past: How a daughter's
OL,4,Cdevotion exposed her mother's murder
OL,6,FHer mother's grave bears an
OL,7,Finscription that Katarzyna composed
OL,8,Fherself: "For the world you were just
OL,9,Fa part, for us you were the whole
OL,10,Fworld." It's a serene setting, about
OL,11,Fas far removed as you could get from
OL,12,Fthe back garden of a terraced house in
OL,13,FDerby. It's taken fifteen years, but
OL,14,Fat long last, Izabela Zablocka has a
OL,15,Fpeaceful and dignified final resting-
OL,16,Fplace.
